{"tid":95472,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【實戰理論】道指破頂 港股高開結算（沈振盈）（JAN 26）","createTime":"2017-01-26T05:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T12:41:55.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bff41702f6e848cbc0796076863bf82d4f0f5c6e","tid":95472,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"【實戰理論】道指破頂 港股高開結算（沈振盈）（JAN 26）<br />\n2017-1-26 8:45:29<br />\n<br />\n千呼萬喚，道指終於上破20000點，收報20068點。過去數天，港股雖然反覆回升，但每日的升幅不多，主要是有盤壓住指數，目的是為了進行期指轉倉，配合今日期指結算，港股勢必高開。美國預託証券及新加坡港股期貨皆高收，估計今早期指會開在23200水平。然而，早上定價後，相信到了中午，市況仍會有一定的波動。長假期前難估計假期後的走勢，皆因外圍變數太多，隱藏的風險不少，筆者相信絶對不會是一般人所認為的風平浪靜。<br />\n<br />\n近期比較強勢的是金融股，渣打（<a href=\"http://02888.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02888.HK&d=yXiVVfE9H8uuJ1DzMtjeyXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9ea1fd75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02888.HK</a>）在過去兩個星期已急升，昨日輪到匯控（<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=yXiVVfE9H8uuJ1DzMtjeyXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7aa7befd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>）有動靜。其股價昨日上升1.47%，收65.50元，重上65元關口。為何看好匯控會接力而上，除了是因為特朗普上台，基本面有改善外，加息令息差擴闊，有利盈利表現之外，短線尚有一個因素，就是英鎊急升，帶來了匯價的推動。技術走勢上，股價重上65元，先挑戰67.5元阻力，上望目標70元。<br />\n<br />\n至於弱勢的股份，仍是以港交所（<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=yXiVVfE9H8uuJ1DzMtjeyXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d5652c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>）最顯著，若然看淡的話，首選港交所。始終指數受太多因素影響，特別是期指結算因素，做好、做淡也有困難，倒不如炒股不炒市。另一個做法，就是運用對沖基金的pair trade策略，call匯控、put港交所，或有可能兩邊贏。<br />\n<br />\n沈振盈"},{"pid":"300f8f5fd5a9f311fdf7f21d6fc0d7cbd358c38f","tid":95472,"uid":182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"388<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baf0ac872504f00e6fbbde753d1cf249352094b","tid":95472,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"//運用對沖基金的pair trade策略，call匯控、put港交所，或有可能兩邊贏。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPut 匯豐<br />\nCall 港交所"},{"pid":"22eeb5b584936222db3293f34d765afdab32d5d3","tid":95472,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/af4207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Faf4207.jpg&h=df543151&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69994c01b1c9418dbf753840a6425df7fd11eb13","tid":95472,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/91231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F91231b.jpg&h=c9f42e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/981125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F981125.jpg&h=af2464e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/929c7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F929c7e.jpg&h=5d808d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/5aba31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F5aba31.jpg&h=5f359a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2e8691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2e8691.jpg&h=75b7357f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/944bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F944bb2.jpg&h=f1cdf002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n